description: Instrumental piano covers of the best songs from the 80's. Cover versions of classic hit songs from 1980 - 1989 featuring Queen, Prince, Michael Jackson, Guns N Roses, Whitney Houston, George Michael, U2, Eurythmics, Elton John, Lionel Richie, Cyndi Lauper, Journey, Bon Jovi, Blondie, ABBA and more.
